### Deploy it

Create an environment to deploy your model:

```shell
$ mlem create env heroku staging
üíæ Saving env to staging.mlem
```

Define the deployment:

```shell
$ mlem create deployment heroku myservice -c app_name=mlem-quick-start -c model=rf -c env=staging
üíæ Saving deployment to myservice.mlem
```

Deploy it:
```shell
$ mlem deploy create myservice
‚è≥Ô∏è Loading deployment from .mlem/deployment/myservice.mlem
üîó Loading link to .mlem/env/staging.mlem
üîó Loading link to .mlem/model/rf.mlem
